                            <comment id="12539711" author="rhillegas" created="Fri, 2 Nov 2007 21:26:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Henrik and Svein Erik. Your changes look like improvements to me. I have committed this patch at subversion revision 591470. In the future, it would be helpful if you could generate your patch from the root directory of the subversion client. The extra path prefixes on the name of the changed file confused my patch tool and I had to strip them off before I could apply the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
